---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { AstroSeo } from "@astrolib/seo";
---

<Base>
  <AstroSeo
    title="Creek CSHS | Cherry Creek Computer Science Honor Society"
    description="offical website of the Cherry Creek Computer Science Honor Society"
  />
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="relative w-full h-[600px] md:h-[800px] lg:h-[1000px]">
      <img
        src="/placeholder.svg"
        width="1200"
        height="800"
        alt=""
        class="absolute inset-0 object-cover w-full h-full"
        style="aspect-ratio: 1200 / 800; object-fit: cover;"
      />
      <div
        class="relative text-black h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4"
      >
        <h1 class="text-black text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold">
          Computer Science Honor Society
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We are a student-run organization that promotes computer science
          education and provides opportunities for students to explore computer
          science outside of the classroom. Our mission is for students to
          contribute to impactful projects, develop their technical skills, and
          build a community of like-minded individuals.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-red-600 px-8 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow transition-colors hover:bg-red-500 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-red-700"
            href="#"
          >
            Apply Now
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-white px-8 text-sm font-medium shadow transition-colors hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-red-700"
            href="#"
          >
            Donate Now
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-white px-8 text-sm font-medium shadow transition-colors hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-red-700"
            href="#"
          >
            Tutoring Timings
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="container px-4 md:px-6 justify-items-center">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center"
        >
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div
              class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-red-600 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-white"
            >
              contribute now!
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl">
              What do we do?
            </h2>
            <p
              class="max-w-[900px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
            >
              Our club can be broken down into three main categories:{" "}
              <strong>Initiatives</strong>, <strong>Interships</strong>, and{
                " "
              }
              <strong>Events</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-6 py-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-12"
        >
          <div
            class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm"
            data-v0-t="card"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Initiatives</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">
                Initiatives are long-term projects that are developed by our
                members. They are a great way to gain experience in software
                development and to work with other students. The unlimate goal
                of each initiative is to provide value and make impact. 2
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm"
            data-v0-t="card"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Events</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">
                Explore our dynamic Events, from coding workshops to tech talks
                and hackathons. Engage with industry leaders, learn new skills,
                and connect with peers in an environment that sparks innovation
                and collaboration
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm"
            data-v0-t="card"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Interships</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">
                Our Internships connect you with leading tech companies for
                real-world experience. From summer roles to part-time positions,
                these opportunities are perfect for applying classroom learning
                and kickstarting your career in technology. We do out best to
                expose our members to the industry.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div
        class="container grid items-center justify-center gap-6 px-4 md:px-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-10"
      >
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter md:text-4xl/tight">
            Membership Benefits
          </h2>
          <p
            class="max-w-[600px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
          >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 min-[400px]:flex-row lg:justify-end">
          <a
            class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-red-600 px-8 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow transition-colors hover:bg-red-500 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-red-700"
            href="#"
          >
            Apply Now
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex text-black h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-white px-8 text-sm font-medium shadow transition-colors hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-red-700"
            href="#"
          >
            Donate Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center"
        >
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div
              class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-red-600 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-white"
            >
              Gallery
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl">
              Our Initiatives
            </h2>
            <p
              class="max-w-[900px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
            >
              Here are some of our initiatives that we are currently working on.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-6 py-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-12"
        >
          <div
            class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm"
            data-v0-t="card"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Open Courseware</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">
                The development of a free and open source courseware for Cherrry
                Creek High School. This initiative includes both the writing of
                the curriculum and the development of the website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm"
            data-v0-t="card"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Tutoring</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">
                We offer free tutoring for students at Cherry Creek High School
                in computer science. We have over 40 tutors that are available
                to help students with any questions they may have.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer
    class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row py-6 w-full shrink-0 items-center px-4 md:px-6 border-t"
  >
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
      Â© Computer Science Honor Socitey. All rights reserved.
    </p>
    <nav class="sm:ml-auto flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
      <a class="text-xs hover:underline underline-offset-4" href="#">
        Donate Now
      </a>
    </nav>
  </footer>
</Base>
